    "description": "<strong>- About the game -</strong><br><br><strong>Pixel Madness</strong> - is simple 2D clicker game but with cool key elements that will help you achieve your goals and make your gameplay more fun.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- You can -</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFTING</h2> - use your workbench to craft different materials from different resources.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRANSMUTATIONS</h2> - use your &quot;Magic knowledge&quot; to splice essences into something very cool.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIFFERENT WORLDS</h2> - visit different locations to obtain better resources with more XP.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOSS FIGHTING</h2> - fight different bosses to earn XP and maybe you can even get a good reward after beating the boss.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WORLDS</h2> - use the unknown power to travel between different worlds to farm even more different resources.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACHIEVEMENTS</h2> - complete goals and unlock cool looking pixel images called achievements.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- More... -</strong></h2><br>Our biggest goal is to make a really good community that is really interested in what we are doing and also wants to be a part of the game development! <br><br>We are going to make a lot of updates in the future with new mechanics/bosses/locations and more, so don't forget to join our official discord server to know about all our announcements &amp; updates!",
